---
/**
 * Hero principal de Space DEV
 * Renderizado 100% en Astro (sin JS)
 */
---

<section id="inicio" class="relative w-full pt-36 pb-40 px-6">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">

      <!-- Columna izquierda -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8">

        <!-- Estado -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-primary/30 bg-primary/5 text-primary text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-primary"></span>
          </span>
          SISTEMA EN LÍNEA: V3.0.0
        </div>

        <!-- Título -->
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tight">
          Si es
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-cosmic-violet">
            código
          </span>,<br />
          es realidad.
        </h1>

        <!-- Descripción -->
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-xl font-light leading-relaxed">
          Ingeniería de fronteras digitales para la próxima generación de pioneros.
          Creamos sistemas de alto rendimiento donde el diseño se encuentra con la precisión matemática.
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
          <button class="group flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-background-dark px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-bold transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,225,255,0.2)]">
            Iniciar Exploración
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">
              arrow_forward
            </span>
          </button>

          <button class="group flex items-center gap-2 border border-white/10 hover:border-primary/50 bg-white/5 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-bold transition-all backdrop-blur-sm">
            Ver Manifiesto
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">
              terminal
            </span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Columna derecha -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 hidden lg:flex flex-col gap-6">

        <!-- Estado del nodo -->
        <div class="glass-panel p-6 rounded-xl space-y-4">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-white/10 pb-2">
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-primary font-bold">
              ESTADO DEL NODO
            </span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xs text-primary">
              sensors
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="data-stream-text text-gray-500 uppercase">LATENCIA_MS</span>
              <span class="data-stream-text text-primary">0.0012</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="data-stream-text text-gray-500 uppercase">SINC_NÚCLEO</span>
              <span class="data-stream-text text-primary">99.9%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="data-stream-text text-gray-500 uppercase">RENDIMIENTO</span>
              <span class="data-stream-text text-primary">4.2 TB/S</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card proyecto -->
        <div class="relative aspect-square rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined icon-web-hero text-[200px] text-white/5 animate-pulse">
              language
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4">
            <div class="p-4 glass-panel rounded-lg flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">
                  rocket_launch
                </span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-tighter">
                  PROYECTO ACTUAL
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase">
                  PROTOCOLO NEBULA
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Indicador scroll -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-32 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 group cursor-pointer animate-bounce-slow">
    <span class="text-primary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-mono">
      DESCUBRE
    </span>
    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(0,225,255,0.6)]">
      expand_more
    </span>
  </div>
</section>
